These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-6-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, iced-tea, sprite
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, gardening, skydiving
The people have 3 different jobs:  lawyer, nurse, police-officer
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: martial-arts, drama, superhero
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, jazz, blues
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, american, pakistani
 1. the police-officer is in an odd position##4
 2. the person drinking mirinda is in the middle##1
 3. the pakistani is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the fan jazz##3
 5. the person watching martial-arts movies is not the person drinking iced-tea##6
 6. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far right##1
 7. the person watching drama movies is in an even position##4
 8. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the right of the fan blues##5
 9. the nurse is between the fan country and the pakistani##2
10. the american is on the left of the lawyer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |      3      |
| Beverage      | sprite        | mirinda        | iced-tea    |
| Hobby         | board-games    | skydiving       | gardening      |
| Job           | police-officer | nurse | lawyer |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts     | drama   | superhero |
| Music-Genre   | country       | blues      | jazz      |
| Nationality   | brazilian   | american      | pakistani     |

