There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, argentine, turkish
3 different pets are kept: snake, rat, frog
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, volleyball, parkour
 1. the turkish is in an odd position##4
 2. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the left of the librarian##5
 3. the argentine is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 4. the person who's sport is volleyball is the canadian##1
 5. the person who's sport is parkour is on the far left##1
 6. the person drinking lemonade is in the middle##1
 7. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 8. the software-developer is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 9. the videographer is not the person who's sport is badminton##6
10. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |       3       |
| Beverage      | fanta         | lemonade        | cola       |
| Hobby         | sudoku | dancing    | gardening   |
| Job           | videographer | librarian     | software-developer         |
| Nationality   | turkish   | argentine   | canadian      |
| Pet           | snake        | frog | rat           |
| Sport         | parkour     | badminton   | volleyball |

