The people prefer 3 different music-genres: folk, salsa, blues
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: sailing, lacrosse, climbing
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, jet-ski, scooter
 1. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an odd position##4
 2. the fan salsa is not the person who's sport is lacrosse##6
 3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3
 4. the person who's sport is climbing is not the fan salsa##6
 5. the pilot is not the fan blues##6
 6. the person watching documentary movies is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is sailing##5
 7. the person driving the scooter is between the person watching drama movies and the person driving the airplane##2
 8. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere to the left of the person watching spy movies##5
 9. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
10. the manager is between the person driving the airplane and the writer##2
11. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
12. the writer is somewhere to the left of the person watching documentary movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3        |
| Hobby         | gardening   | reading  | photography     |
| Job           | writer | manager   | pilot |
