The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, documentary, mystery
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, mouse, guinea-pig
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: ice-hockey, parkour, swimming
 1. the person eating plum is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##5
 2. the person watching disaster movies is not the person who's sport is swimming##6
 3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not the owner of the chinchilla##6
 4. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the right of the person drinking 7up##5
 5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person eating potato##1
 6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 7. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 8. the person who's hobby is chess is not the person drinking hot-chocolate##6
 9. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
10. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not the person watching disaster movies##6
11. the person watching mystery movies is the person eating pomegranate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |
