.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-6-17::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, water, 7up
There 3 different types of food: strawberry, carrot, banana
The people have 3 different jobs:  mechanic, project-manager, nurse
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, disaster, satire
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: soccer, skateboarding, cricket
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, car, trike
 1. the project-manager is in an even position##4
 2. the person driving the trike is on the far right##1
 3. the person watching satire movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating banana##5
 4. the person watching animation movies is the person driving the car##1
 5. the person eating banana is on the far left##1
 6. the person drinking 7up is not the person who's sport is cricket##6
 7. the person drinking water is on the right of the mechanic##1
 8. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left or right of the person watching disaster movies##3
 9. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer##3
10. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left or right of the person eating carrot##3
11. the person who's sport is cricket is somewhere to the right of the person driving the boat##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |       2        |      3      |
| Beverage      | 7up | water          | juice |
| Food          | banana        | carrot     | strawberry |
| Job           | mechanic        | project-manager | nurse   |
| Movie-Genre   | animation         | disaster          | satire |
| Sport         | skateboarding      | soccer     | cricket  |
| Transport     | car       | boat            | trike       |

