.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-6-18::.
There 3 different types of food: plum, cucumber, corn
The people have 3 different jobs:  photographer, social-worker, videographer
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: documentary, zombie, disaster
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, reggae, gospel
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, parkour, rugby
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, van, motorbike
 1. the videographer is not the person eating cucumber##6
 2. the person driving the van is not the fan classical##6
 3. the social-worker is on the far left##1
 4. the fan gospel is somewhere to the left of the person driving the van##5
 5. the person driving the van is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is parkour##5
 6. the fan classical is the person watching disaster movies##1
 7. the person eating corn is on the right of the person eating plum##1
 8. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere to the left of the person watching zombie movies##5
 9. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
10. the person eating plum is on the left or right of the person watching documentary movies##3
11. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the van##5
12. the videographer is the person driving the van##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |
| Food          | cucumber   | plum | corn |
| Job           | social-worker    | videographer  | photographer |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary     | zombie | disaster |
| Music-Genre   | gospel       | reggae   | classical    |
| Sport         | rugby | biathlon | parkour |
| Transport     | car      | van    | motorbike        |

