.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-6-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, lemonade, water
There 3 different types of food: raspberry, onion, plum
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, house, punk
3 different pets are kept: rabbit, lizard, fish
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: weightlifting, rowing, badminton
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, motorbike, bus
 1. the fan blues is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the right of the person driving the motorbike##5
 3. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is rowing##5
 4. the person drinking water is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 5. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 6. the person eating raspberry is the person driving the quad-bike##1
 7. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the fan punk##1
 8. the person eating plum is in the middle##1
 9. the owner of the fish is not the person drinking lemonade##6
10. the fan house is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |
| Beverage      | water     | lemonade      | iced-tea       |
| Food          | onion   | plum | raspberry  |
| Music-Genre   | punk    | house       | blues |
| Pet           | rabbit        | lizard        | fish     |
| Sport         | rowing    | badminton | weightlifting  |
| Transport     | motorbike | bus      | quad-bike  |

 